flowchart LR
    A[Developer Push or Manual Dispatch] --> B[CI Job]
    B --> C{Tests and Lint Pass?}

    C -- Yes --> D[Pipeline Green]
    C -- No --> E[Capture and Upload ci_failure.log]

    E --> F[self_heal Job]
    F --> G[LangGraph collect_failure]
    G --> H[analyze_root_cause]
    H --> I[propose_code_fix\nRule-based + Optional LLM]
    I --> J{Fix Found and Applied?}

    J -- No --> K[No-op with Decision Summary]
    J -- Yes --> L[validate_fix\nRe-run pytest and ruff]

    L --> M{Validation Passed?}
    M -- No --> N{attempt < max_attempts?}
    N -- Yes --> I
    N -- No --> K

    M -- Yes --> O{PR Gates\nToken + Changed + Event}
    O -- No --> K
    O -- Yes --> P[Create or Update Auto-fix PR]

    P --> Q[Reviewer Approves and Merges]
    Q --> D
